<plot>Experts estimate that there are more tigers in private captivity in the USA than there are roaming wild in the world. 24 of them live in Dennis H's backyard. The Tiger Next Door follows the story of one man who has been keeping, breeding, and selling tigers from his backyard in Flat Rock, Indiana for over fifteen years.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?596032</url></doc>
